FBIS3-16597 "drsov053_r_94005" FBIS-SOV-94-053 Document Type:Daily Report 17 Mar 1994 Azerbaijan TV Broadcast Hours Cut By Electricity Shortage LD1703161494 Moscow Radio Rossii Network in Russian 1400 GMT 17 Mar 94 LD1703161494 Moscow Radio Rossii Network Language: Russian Article Type:BFN [Text] According to RIA, broadcasting of daytime television programs in Azerbaijan has been cut by two hours because of a shortage of electricity. The management of the republic's state television and radio company is not ruling out the possibility of further cuts or even a complete halt to television broadcasts during the day on all television channels, including commercial
